Package: nanolx-x11
Architecture: all
Depends: compton,
         conky-std,
         fehlstart,
         lightdm,
         lightdm-gtk-greeter,
         lightdm-gtk-greeter-settings,
         rep (>= 0.92),
         rep-gtk (>= 0.90),
         sawfish (>= 1.9.1),
         sawfish-pager (>= 0.90),
         ssd (>= 0.40),
         x11-xserver-utils,
         konsole,
         gucharmap,
         xarchiver,
         yad,
         qt5-configuration-tool,
         trayer,
         gtk3-nocsd
Description: Collection of X11 applications
 This meta-package installs extra X11 applications on the system.
 .
 These are:
 - compton
 - conky
 - gucharmap
 - fehlstart
 - lightdm (with gtk-greeter and settings editor)
 - librep (with gtk-binding)
 - sawfish (with pager and session-dialog)
 - x11-xserver-utils
 - konsole
 - xarchiver
 - YAD (GTK+ Dialogs from shell scripts)
 - Qt5 Configuration Tool
 - Trayer
 - GTK+3 no client side decoration (CSD)

